Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 14 November 2016. Image shows Chanakya (ancient Indian political strategist) — bald head, rudraksha beads, pointing finger — with Hindi text: 'Gaddaron ki toli mein yadi hahakar ho to samajh lo desh ka raja mahan aur charitravan hai aur desh pragati path par teevra agrasar hai.' Translation: 'If there is outcry among the gang of traitors, understand that the king of the nation is great and virtuous, and the country is swiftly progressing on the path of development.' Timestamp visible: 10:12 AM. Post-demonetization message supporting PM Modi through Chanakya's wisdom. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Divine Justice — comparing Modi's demonetization to a righteous king's bold action.